Megavideo Link Cleaner
Version 1.0 by PicciMario <mario.piccinelli@gmail.com>
Released under MIT license. Enjoy!

Usage: regen.py [-u megavideourl | -c megavideocode]

Other options:
-d	Debug info
-v	Verbose (still less thank DEBUG)
-l N	Limit the output to the first N found links (>=1!)

If you supply the megavideocode, the url will be formatted
as http://www.megavideo.com/?v=XXXXX.

If you do not use v (verbose) or d (debug), the tool only prints
out the found url(s) (or the supplied url if this is valid)
